### Contacts REST tests

### Get all contacts
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts

### Get a single contact (replace :id with a real id from the previous response)
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts/:id

### Create a new contact
POST http://localhost:3000/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "João",
    "lastName": "Silva",
    "email": "joao@example.com",
    "favoriteColor": "blue",
    "birthday": "1990-01-01"
}

### Update a contact (replace :id with a real id)
PUT http://localhost:3000/contacts/:id
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "João",
    "lastName": "Silva",
    "email": "joao.silva@example.com",
    "favoriteColor": "green",
    "birthday": "1990-01-01"
}

### Delete a contact (replace :id with a real id)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/contacts/:id
